      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, primarily as a project car or for parts. The engine requires a major overhaul due to significant oil leaks and a persistent knocking sound, and the transmission shifts harshly. Externally, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling across most surfaces. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard, and the air conditioning is currently non-functional. It will need significant work to be roadworthy again.",
